creator: Sikabu Studio
descriptionHtml:
Lalisa Manobal, known mononymously as Lisa, is a Thai rapper, singer and dancer based in South Korea. She is a member of the South Korean girl group Blackpink formed by YG Entertainment. Lisa made her solo debut with her single album Lalisa in September 2021.

This application is made for the lovers of Lalisa Manoban. With a friendly user interface and easy to use.


HOW TO USE
1. Open Lalisa Manoban Wallpaper application
2. Choose picture the best one.
3. Click "Wallpaper" to edit (rotate, scale) photo before apply.
4. Click "Download" to save the photo to your phone gallery.
5. Click "Share" if you want to share the photo on social media, chat and etc.
6. Click "Fullscreen" if you want to view the photo in full-screen mode.
7. Click "Favorite" to save your favorite picture.


APPLICATION ADVANTAGES
• Photos always keep up-to-date.
• High-quality photos (Full HD, 4K).
• 100% Free.
• Easy to use.
• Favorite collection.
• Category collection.
• Autofit wallpaper to your device resolution.

DISCLAIMER
This application is made by Lalisa Manoban fans and is unofficial. The content in this app is not affiliated with, endorsed, sponsored, or specifically approved by any company. This app just for all fans who want to enjoy these Lisa Manoban wallpaper. If we have violated any copyright by use of any images included in this app, please notify us at sikabustudio@outlook.com and we shall promptly remove it. Thank you.
